{"tid":1534591,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"過左三個月 仲有人信和平示威可以贏到？","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:18:02.000Z","uid":126153,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"edd66b4af16e97bf695545107b05bf8589554ae8","tid":1534591,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"仲有人主張打長久戰 咁同左膠永續社運有乜分別<br />\n呢啲人唔屌 反而屌我分化<br />\n我真係唔知仲有咩方法可以令和理非拎起武器<br />\n三個月啦 一齊進步下好無？"},{"pid":"a07c6eff79dbce9ddeb7930507c01c8f3c3c4a66","tid":1534591,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a568cf41d0164c057a1dd6362087e5cc7b1c6073","tid":1534591,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=27a9e90d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"4eae1a449ad523dfaeabb7f4a93d31b7c3fb845b","tid":1534591,"uid":307196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"長期戰一定要靠和理非"},{"pid":"77d6063de95b7e81f2708c60e426aabbdba42484","tid":1534591,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ec6878388197ee23ad791db6a2d874c685b78c6","tid":1534591,"uid":230849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"成班廢青喺度搞屎搞棍 夠薑你就衝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495acb3ce69ae898ac762f2adda3a40241ba69b8","tid":1534591,"uid":300690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"政府警察攞明犯法，邊個拉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e23573f407efd1ce923aa8c918bffe36d8cbb2","tid":1534591,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"呢個post我改一改口 唔屌和理非<br />\n我只想你地諗一諗<br />\n係唔係對住依家個政府 仲要講仁義道德"},{"pid":"e1bcddfb0ec4d8350342a7cc9e2fbf521109c590","tid":1534591,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"270c42cadc0fd343c9f303d69f97260b18d780ae","tid":1534591,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1bcddfb0ec4d8350342a7cc9e2fbf521109c590","tid":1534591,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"係一種手段 但絕對唔應該成為主流<br />\n如果唔係個個都拖 個政府就係想睇我地拖到收自己皮"},{"pid":"97487f2024a74744647479a646884271aae291d5","tid":1534591,"uid":265904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"過左三個月 仲有人覺得係香港,勇武示威可以贏到？<br />\n仲有人主張次次END GAME 咁同自殺有咩分別, 拉左成千個手足, <br />\n又傷又爆眼, 對家零傷害, 政府reject 所有demand<br />\n我真係唔知仲有咩方法可以令勇武試下放低武器用其他方法。<br />\n三個月啦 一齊反思下好無？"},{"pid":"4172cc5d